unique_ptr: create, reset , reset with value, reset with make_unique(preferred), move, pass ptr as argument(value & reference) and return parameter, get()
shared_ptr: create multip1e copies, reset original and check value and reference count, cyclic reference example.
weak_ptr: create, solve cyclic reference, expired(), lock(), when does weak_ptr expire?, convert to shared pointer, create shared ptr copy and check reference count, now reset original and check.
